data.description: Welcome to HOME!  2-story home offers a harmonious blend of spacious living and elegant design. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a generous living room, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. Adjacent, is a separate dining room. The kitchen features stunning light fixtures that illuminate the room. A sunroom bathed in natural light invites you to unwind and relax. Connecting to the sunrooms is a lush and private patio area that offers an oasis for outdoor gatherings or quiet moments viewing the large flat backyard. A spacious 2-car garage ensures convenience. This is more than a house; it's your next chapter waiting to be written. With a full price offer seller will do a $8,500 painting allowance
